\u00e5 for barna i R\u00f8ros.", "- N\u00e5r det er s\u00e5nn som i dag er vi ikke ute. Det er nesten tredve minus n\u00e5, forteller Haave.", "- Hva er dr\u00f8mmev\u00e6ret for dere da?", "- Vi har hatt en kuldeperiode n\u00e5 i januar s\u00e5 det har blitt uvanlig lite uteaktivitet. Vi \u00f8nsker oss litt mer sn\u00f8 og ti minus, det er dr\u00f8mmevinteren for oss."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "vaeret"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "176b77ccec8e95edc5d1cad0238892a4fe2883eb7e64919c9ec5bd5c6997254a"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2016-01-14T16:40:31.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "- At barna her er fremavla som spesielt kuldehardf\u00f8re tror jeg ikke, sier kommuneoverlegen i R\u00f8ros."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article12027372.ece/1gpcii/ALTERNATES/w980-default/galaaen-naturbarnehage1.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/da18f7be5bfaff6fcc1034d29c0fb2a6c1ebae4a.jpg?58f9de76"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["Her vil barna ut selv om det er under 20 minusgrader -adressa.no", "Ull innerst og p\u00e5 med lua", "Dr\u00f8mmev\u00e6ret"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "da18f7be5bfaff6fcc1034d29c0fb2a6c1ebae4a"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["v\u00e6ret", "R\u00f8ros", "Barnehage"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "v\u00e6ret,R\u00f8ros,Barnehage"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": "vaeret"}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "family-and-parenting"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["barn", "ull innerst", "spesielt kuldehardf\u00f8re"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": "gal\u00e5en"}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": "r\u00f8ros"}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": ["lindis haave", "helge lund"]}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "value": "vaeret"}, {"field": 